text: Kubyakovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kunakbayevsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 12 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Uchaly, 22 km from Kunakbayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Kubyakovo
